         <p style="text-align: center;">(Ensure your safety. This Organization will not be responsible for any inconvenience.)</p>
         <p style="color: gray; font-style:italic; text-align: center;">We are constantly struggling to collect blood for the dying patients. It is our responsibility 
            to manage the blood of patients in an emergency, as well as to ensure the safety of a blood donor.
      </p>
