              <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-stretch" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <!-- <div class="icon"><i class="bx bxl-dribbble"></i></div> -->
                  <img src="https://www.donatebloodbd.com/images/donors-Bangladesh.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="" data-aos="zoom-in">
                  <hr>
                  <h4 class="title"><a href="" style="color: rgb(224, 53, 53);">Telling the Blood Donors</a></h4>
                  <p class="description">
                    <ul>
                      <li style="text-align: left;">Find out which hospital/clinic the patient is in. Do not donate blood anywhere other than hospital/clinic. Not even at the patient's home.</li>
                      <li style="text-align: left;">Do not meet the blood applicant (the person you are contacting on the mobile number) anywhere other than the hospital/clinic. Do not ask to meet in the alley next to the hospital, or in a shop.</li>
                      <li style="text-align: left;">Check the patient before donating blood. Check the patient's report, doctor's requisition letter.</li>
                      <li style="text-align: left;">It is better to have two friends with you when donating blood.</li>
                      <li style="text-align: left;">Make sure to use new needles when donating blood...</li>
                      <li style="text-align: left;">If in doubt about the competence of the attending expert, inform the authority...</li>
                      <li style="text-align: left;">Donate after blood cross matching, not before... most govt hospitals keep blood without cross matching... it should never be done... self aware... donate blood after cross matching...</li>
                    </ul>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
      
              <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-stretch" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="200">
